WEBVTT

00:08:28.440 --> 00:08:31.296
in my case more than 2,000 of them,

00:08:31.320 --> 00:08:33.440
and some were quite personal.

00:08:34.400 --> 00:08:36.616
And to make matters worse,

00:08:36.640 --> 00:08:38.696
when we read the terms and conditions,

00:08:38.720 --> 00:08:40.096
we discovered the following,

00:08:40.120 --> 00:08:43.240
and I'm going to need to take out
my reading glasses for this one.

00:08:44.400 --> 00:08:47.336
And I'm going to read it for you,
because this is complicated.

00:08:47.360 --> 00:08:48.560
All right.

00:08:49.440 --> 00:08:50.976
"By posting content" --

00:08:51.000 --> 00:08:52.976
and content refers to your pictures, chat

00:08:53.000 --> 00:08:55.216
and other interactions
in the dating service --

00:08:55.240 --> 00:08:56.496
"as a part of the service,

00:08:56.520 --> 00:08:58.496
you automatically grant to the company,

00:08:58.520 --> 00:09:00.696
its affiliates, licensees and successors